Package: argonaut-fuse
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, argonaut-common (>= 1.0), argonaut-fuse-fai, liblog-handler-perl, libconfig-inifiles-perl, ucf, libfuse-perl, libfile-pid-perl, libnet-ldap-perl, fuse-utils
Recommends: tftpd | atftpd | tftpd-hpa
Description: Modular TFTP/Fuse supplicant
 Argonaut-fuse is a modular fuse-tftp-supplicant written in perl which allows
 to create pxelinux configurations for different types of clients
 using external modules
 . 
 There is already written modules for FAI (Fully automated install).

Package: argonaut-fuse-fai
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libnet-ldap-perl, argonaut-fuse
Description: LDAP FAI module for the TFTP/Fuse supplicant
 FAI module for argonaut-fuse which is using the LDAP backend in conjunction
 with FusionDirectory and Argonaut to generate client configurations.
 .

Package: argonaut-fuse-opsi
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libjson-perl (>= 2.07-1), libjson-rpc-perl, argonaut-fuse
Description: LDAP OPSI module for the TFTP/Fuse supplicant
 OPSI module for argonaut-fuse which is using the opsi json-rpc backend in conjunction
 with FusionDirectory and Argonaut to generate client configurations.
 .
 
Package: argonaut-fuse-ltsp
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libnet-ldap-perl, argonaut-fuse
Description: LDAP LTSP module for the TFTP/Fuse supplicant
 LTSP module for argonaut-fuse which is using the LDAP in conjunction
 with FusionDirectory and Argonaut to generate client configurations.
 .
